  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102680/extras/e7941768a50399ea6353a86749338a48.poster.avif?t=1745476100\" width=504 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102680/extras/e7941768a50399ea6353a86749338a48.webm?t=1745476100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102680/extras/e7941768a50399ea6353a86749338a48.mp4?t=1745476100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Blinded by Fear is a LiDAR horror game with an anxiety inducing atmosphere. Your sight stolen. Your freedom taken. In it's place, is LiDAR, a light detection and ranging scanner that samples the world one dot at a time.<br><br>Reveal your environment as you explore. Solve puzzles, avoid hazards and uncover the mystery of the Anima. An abandoned scientific research facility with a dark secret and even darker terrors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102680/extras/bad84f5550147a00f6563578bc26d2f1.poster.avif?t=1745476100\" width=544 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102680/extras/bad84f5550147a00f6563578bc26d2f1.webm?t=1745476100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102680/extras/bad84f5550147a00f6563578bc26d2f1.mp4?t=1745476100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br>- A novel LiDAR mechanic. Explore the world with a LiDAR scanner.<br>- A compelling story and mystery to uncover and unfold.<br>- Puzzle and Stealth elements. Avoid the hazards lurking in the Anima Research Station.<br>- A full blown level editor and Steam Workshop support.<br>- Steam deck ready!<br><br><strong>Community</strong><br><br>Join us on Discord! <br><br><br><br>If you have any issues please message on Discord or on the Steam community page.",
